'''RenTrans''' was a major shipping organization in the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core]] that existed during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The corporation was at one time owned by the [[Rendar family]], before being sold to rival [[Xizor Transport Systems/Legends|Xizor Transport Systems]].

